    "biomes": ["forest"],
    "weight": 9,
    "one_shot": false,
    "text": "You arrive to find it already happening—three bandits have a merchant family stopped on the road. The merchant is arguing. His wife has gone quiet in the way people go quiet when they've realized arguing won't help.",
